aRqCZUsX","ref":"Lev.18.1","text":"And the LORD spake unto Moses, saying,","year":-1490},{"id":"recr8xJilzVqfuME8","ref":"Lev.18.2","text":"Speak unto the children of Israel, and say unto them, I am the LORD your God.","year":-1490},{"id":"recupqK4KFSNFy0iw","ref":"Lev.18.3","text":"After the doings of the land of Egypt, wherein ye dwelt, shall ye not do: and after the doings of the land of Canaan, whither I bring you, shall ye not do: neither shall ye walk in their ordinances.","year":-1490},{"id":"recT6vPriFaLLVxwW","ref":"Lev.18.4","text":"Ye shall do my judgments, and keep mine ordinances, to walk therein: I am the LORD your God.","year":-1490},{"id":"recTVIROMMNtT7mZ4","ref":"Lev.18.5","text":"Ye shall therefore keep my statutes, and my judgments: which if a man do, he shall live in them: I am the LORD.","year":-1490},{"id":"reck67HOPbZJyxmzf","ref":"Lev.18.6","text":"None of you shall approach to any that is near of kin to him, to uncover their nakedness: I am the LORD.","year":-1490},{"id":"recjkbbnZbFOUVQuN","ref":"Lev.18.7","text":"The nakedness of thy father, or the nakedness of thy mother, shalt thou not uncover: she is thy mother; thou shalt not uncover her nakedness.","year":-1490},{"id":"recDsdUGbJW4tMJ9j","ref":"Lev.18.8","text":"The nakedness of thy father’s wife shalt thou not uncover: it is thy father’s nakedness.","year":-1490}]}
